  ('promotion-d1056197-moex-00076', 'promotion-d1056197', 'promotion-d1056197-moex-112-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-promotion-d1056197-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據簡單凱因斯模型的架構，當邊際儲蓄傾向為0.2時，下列敘述何者正確？', '["平均消費傾向為0.8", "政府支出增加的乘數效果為10", "邊際消費傾向高於邊際儲蓄傾向", "政府支出增加所產生的排擠效果為5"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5f8ef5676876", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6da727d55af5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112170", "c": "105", "s": "0906", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員升官等考試、112年關務人員升官等考試、112年交通事業鐵路人員升資考試、112年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "僑務行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('promotion-d1056197-moex-00077', 'promotion-d1056197', 'promotion-d1056197-moex-112-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-promotion-d1056197-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據凱因斯學派的名目工資具向下僵固性，下列何種現象代表勞動市場未處在均衡狀態？', '["非自願性失業為零", "若總合需求增加，產出不變，物價上升", "若總合需求減少，產出不變，物價下跌", "若總合需求增加，產出及物價皆上升"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5f8ef5676876", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6da727d55af5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112170", "c": "105", "s": "0906", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員升官等考試、112年關務人員升官等考試、112年交通事業鐵路人員升資考試、112年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "僑務行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('promotion-d1056197-moex-00078', 'promotion-d1056197', 'promotion-d1056197-moex-112-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-promotion-d1056197-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關總體經濟模型，下列敘述何者正確？', '["IS-LM模型描繪價格水準與實質GDP之關係", "AD-AS模型描繪價格水準與實質GDP之關係", "凱因斯交叉模型（Keynesiancrossmodel）描繪價格水準與實質GDP之關係", "Mundell-Fleming模型描繪價格水準與實質GDP之關係"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5f8ef5676876", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6da727d55af5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112170", "c": "105", "s": "0906", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員升官等考試、112年關務人員升官等考試、112年交通事業鐵路人員升資考試、112年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "僑務行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('promotion-d1056197-moex-00079', 'promotion-d1056197', 'promotion-d1056197-moex-112-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-promotion-d1056197-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '小明是位社會新鮮人，同時也是沒有耐心（impatient）的消費者，根據新古典學派的消費理論模 型並在自然對數（naturallogarithm）效用函數下，則小明的消費成長率（consumptiongrowthrate） 將會：', '["相對較高", "相對較低", "和利率成反向關係", "只取決於未來所得總額"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5f8ef5676876", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6da727d55af5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112170", "c": "105", "s": "0906", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員升官等考試、112年關務人員升官等考試、112年交通事業鐵路人員升資考試、112年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "僑務行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
